Annotation Interface Inject

@Target(FIELD) @Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface Inject
Fields annotated with Inject will be assigned a value that is provided by a Produces method. If no Producer for the field type is available then the field will be assigned null. Please note, that each field type can only have one producer.
